## Empty

---



[Fluid Condition Type](https://origins.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/fluid_condition_types/empty)

Checks whether there is no fluid in this state.

Type ID: `origins:empty`




---

### Examples

```json
"fluid_condition": {
    "type": "origins:empty"
}
```
